1. HOTEL
Attributes: hotelID, name, address, phoneNumber, starRating, totalRooms
Operations: getRoomAvailability()

2. GUEST
Attributes: guestID, firstName, lastName, email, phoneNumber, password, dateOfBirth, registrationDate
Operations: makeReservation(), cancelBooking(), leaveReview()

3. RESERVATION
Attributes: bookingReference, checkInDate, checkOutDate, numberOfAdults, numberOfChildren, totalAmount, status, createdDate
Operations: calculateTotal(), confirmBooking(), cancel()

4. ROOM
Attributes: roomNumber, floor, status, pricePerNight, maxOccupancy, hasBalcony
Operations: checkAvailability(), updateStatus(), calculatePrice()

5. ROOM TYPE
Attributes: roomTypeID, typeName, description, basePrice, bedConfiguration, maxGuests
Operations: getRoomDetails()

6. PAYMENT
Attributes: paymentID, amount, paymentDate, paymentMethod, transactionReference, status, cardLast4Digits
Operations: processPayment(), refundPayment()

7. INVOICE
Attributes: invoiceNumber, issueDate, totalAmount, taxAmount, isPaid
Operations: generateInvoice()

8. REVIEW
Attributes: reviewID, rating, cleanlinessRating, comfortRating, comment, reviewDate, isVerified
Operations: submitReview()

9. AMENITY
Attributes: amenityID, name, description, category
Operations: getAmenityDetails()

10. SPECIAL REQUEST
Attributes: requestID, requestType, description, status, requestDate
Operations: processRequest()

11. CHECK-IN RECORD
Attributes: checkInID, checkInDateTime, keyCardsIssued, idVerified, depositPaid
Operations: recordCheckIn(), generateInvoice()

12. STAFF (superclass)
Attributes: staffID, firstName, lastName, email, phoneNumber, role, hireDate
Operations: performDuty()

13. RECEPTIONIST (inherits from Staff)
Attributes: shiftTiming, deskNumber
Operations: checkInGuest(), checkOutGuest(), assignRoom()

14. HOUSEKEEPING STAFF (inherits from Staff)
Attributes: assignedFloors, supervisorID
Operations: updateRoomStatus(), reportMaintenance()

15. MANAGER (inherits from Staff)
Attributes: department, authorisationLevel
Operations: generateReports(), viewAnalytics()
